## Early game

Somatic Fibers is a **Lua regional drop**, dropped by **Sentient
Demolishers** on the Moon's Disruption node, **Apollo**. Run Disruption
rounds and clear Demolishers as they spawn to farm a steady trickle alongside
your conduit defense duties. These are in-mission enemy drops, so a
**Resource Drop Booster does boost them**.

The main early-game reason to farm Somatic Fibers is crafting **Lua Lenses**,
so plan a handful of Apollo runs whenever you're pushing focus school progress
rather than treating it as a background farm.

## Mid & late game

**Steel Path Apollo** is the sustained endgame farm: Demolishers hit harder
but still drop the same fibers, and the Steel Path Resource Drop Chance
Booster stacks with a regular booster on every Demolisher kill. Running
Disruption for full rounds (not just rushing conduits) maximizes Demolisher
spawns and therefore Somatic Fibers per hour.

Since the resource is scoped to a single node, there's no alternate mission
type to rotate into if you tire of Disruption — Apollo is the farm.

